Wiimotedev-project is a collection of wiimotedev sub-projects, for more information go
to wiimotedev-project webside (http://code.google.com/p/wiimotedev/) or visit the official 
channel #wiimotedev on irc.freenode.net 

This version by default use static version of libcwiid, if you want to disable this
feature please use -DUSE_STATIC_CWIID=OFF flag

In oder to compile, run:

# cmake . -DDISTRO=yourdistro -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr
# make all
# make install

Requirement: Qt4 Libraries, Bluez